column26: Get UK Police & Courts to look into Amber Heard Perjury Charges
column33: Get UK Police & Courts to look into Amber Heard Perjury Charges
column34:
Amber Heard gave evidence under OATH in the UK in July 2020. 

Evidence has come to light that shows she knowingly made these statements dispite them being false.  She has used our judicial system to further her career thus allowing for financial gain.

The UK Police and Courts should look into the new evidence and bring charged if they find any wrong doing

We think that this injustice should be rectified as no one is above the law of the courts. And to lie under oath to make themselves look better and for financial gain is a travesty. They think they are above the law when we need to show them they are NOT. The British public stand behind their countries LAW

column33: Get UK Police & Courts to look into Amber Heard Perjury Charges
column34:
Amber Heard gave evidence under OATH in the UK in July 2020. 

Evidence has come to light that shows she knowingly made these statements dispite them being false.  She has used our judicial system to further her career thus allowing for financial gain.

The UK Police and Courts should look into the new evidence and bring charged if they find any wrong doing

We think that this injustice should be rectified as no one is above the law of the courts. And to lie under oath to make themselves look better and for financial gain is a travesty. They think they are above the law when we need to show them they are NOT. The British public stand behind their countries LAW
